snippet: The 2003 P.G.A. Championship winner, Shaun Micheel, trying to end a nine-year winless drought since then, shot a five-under 67 to lead the Spanish Open in Seville.
abstract: Shaun Micheel takes first-round lead at Spanish Open golf tournament.
lead_paragraph: The 2003 P.G.A. Championship winner, Shaun Micheel, trying to end a nine-year winless drought since then, shot a five-under 67 to lead the Spanish Open in Seville.
